{"tid":1518361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好再約人十點","createTime":"2019-08-30T08:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:07:46.000Z","uid":228624,"like":4,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf0653d81a735874f6acee73b642f7a0b802ea41","tid":1518361,"uid":228624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"一到十點叫口號 叫一至兩個鐘<br />\n叫一晚半晚都算 訓少兩個鐘冇所謂<br />\n但係宜家大概都連續叫左5-6日<br />\n其實樓上D人都要訓覺休息<br />\n你咁樣係想達到咩目的呢？<br />\n宜家係精神折磨緊樓上D居民呀<br />\n唔係話不割𥱊就可以做乜都得<br />\n希望你地可以考慮返附近居民嘅感受<br />\n不論你是否住係喱個屋苑<br />\n唔好再用咪用喇叭用擴音器用電筒照入人地屋企<br />\n感謝各位<br />\n<br />\n利申 絕對支持反修例 支持成立獨立調查小組查popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b9f39d28f58710f803e3a3c40e0cbadf70ecbb","tid":1518361,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUivSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=484de548\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUivSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=214db0e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUivSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=d64d5d21\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4f66c6e1366e28ef1ee98087c72ceaa1cac859fc","tid":1518361,"uid":233316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:33:45.000Z","ms